# Intelligent App Review Sentiment Analyzer

## Overview
This project is a Machine Learning based web application that analyzes app reviews and predicts whether the sentiment is positive or negative.

The application was built using Python and Streamlit, with a focus on text preprocessing and sentiment classification.

---

## Features
- Predicts sentiment of app reviews
- Interactive Streamlit interface
- Text preprocessing and cleaning
- Real-time sentiment prediction

---

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Streamlit
- Scikit-learn
- NLP (Natural Language Processing)
- Joblib

---

## Project Workflow
1. Data Cleaning & Text Preprocessing
2. Model Training
3. Sentiment Prediction
4. Streamlit App Development
5. Deployment

---

## How It Works
The user enters an app review into the application.  
The text is cleaned and processed before being passed into the trained machine learning model, which predicts whether the review sentiment is positive or negative.

---

## Project Files
- app.py
- sentiment.pkl
- Intelligent App Review System.ipynb
- requirements.txt

